languages.text: "Я в порядке, элантах". {n}Благосклонный взгляд и легкая улыбка служат подкреплением словам эльдарки.{/n} "Благодаря тебе я наконец достигла конца своего Пути. Этого Пути. И я благодарна, что ты прош{mf|ел|ла} по нему вместе со мной".

"I am fine, elantach." {n}A gracious look and a slight smile underscore Yrliet's words.{/n} "Thanks to you, I have finally reached the end of my Path. This Path. And I am grateful I had you to walk alongside me."

languages.text: «Estoy bien, elantach». {n}Yrliet subraya sus palabras con una mirada gentil y una leve sonrisa.{/n} «Gracias a ti, por fin he alcanzado el final de mi senda. De esta senda. Y estoy agradecida por haberla recorrido contigo a mi lado».

languages.text: “我很好，外界人。”{n}伊莉耶特眼神亲切，淡淡地微笑道。{/n}“多亏了你，我终于抵达了这条道途的尽头。我很高兴有你陪在我身边。”
languages.original_text: "I am fine, elantach." {n}A gracious look and a slight smile underscore Yrliet's words.{/n} "Thanks to you, I have finally reached the end of my Path. This Path. And I am grateful I had you to walk alongside me."

languages.text: {n}Yrliet vous répond avec un regard bienveillant et un léger sourire :{/n} « Je vais bien, elantach. Grâce à vous, j'ai enfin atteint l'aboutissement de ma Voie... de cette Voie. Et je vous suis reconnaissante de m'avoir accompagnée. »
languages.original_text: "I am fine, elantach." {n}A gracious look and a slight smile underscore Yrliet's words.{/n} "Thanks to you, I have finally reached the end of my Path. This Path. And I am grateful I had you to walk alongside me."

languages.text: 「大丈夫だ、エランタ」{n}丁重な外観とかすかな微笑みが、ユリエットの言葉を際立たせる。{/n}「あなたのおかげで、私はついにこの道の終わりにたどり着いた。この道を。あなたと一緒に歩めたことを感謝している」
languages.original_text: "I am fine, elantach." {n}A gracious look and a slight smile underscore Yrliet's words.{/n} "Thanks to you, I have finally reached the end of my Path. This Path. And I am grateful I had you to walk alongside me."

languages.text: "Mir geht es gut, Elantach." {n}Ein dankbarer Blick und ein leichtes Lächeln unterstreichen Yrliets Worte ...{/n} "Dank Euch habe ich endlich das Ende meines Pfades erreicht. Dieses Pfades. Und ich bin dankbar, dass Ihr ihn mit mir gemeinsam beschritten habt."

languages.text: "İyiyim elantach." {n}Yrliet'in sözlerini zarif bir bakış ve hafif bir gülümseme tamamlıyor.{/n} "Sayende Yolumun... Bu Yolun sonuna nihayet erişebildim. Senin de bu Yolda bana eşlik etmenden dolayı minnettarım."
